    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Alias
    Represents an alternative name for a show or episode name.
    Alias.AliasBuilder

    AlternateEpisode.AlternateEpisodeBuilder<C,B>
     
    AlternateEpisode.EmbeddedResource
    The possible embedded resource types that can be included in an AlternateEpisode.
    AlternateEpisode.EmbeddedResource.EmbeddedResourceBuilder
     
    AlternateEpisode.EmbeddedType
    The supported embedded resource types that can be included in an AlternateEpisode.
    AlternateList
    Defines different types of episode lists for a tv show (e.g.,., differing order and/or releases in one region vs. another, etc.).
    AlternateList.AlternateListBuilder<C,B>
     
    AlternateList.EmbeddedResource
    The possible embedded resource types that can be included in an AlternateList.
    AlternateList.EmbeddedResource.EmbeddedResourceBuilder
     
    AlternateList.EmbeddedType
    The supported embedded resource types that can be included in an AlternateList.
    ApiBase
    The API Base class used to simplify the construction of API URLs for the Connection.
